                                    <p>This is my tiny corner of the Internet where I celebrate my life &amp; personal interests. Here, you'll find a collection of art, musings and other things I find fun! This site is also a homage to the old web, a space where I hope to separate myself from the constraints and toxicity of social media in a space entirely my own.</p>
